{"image_id": "UNM_2015_page_119", "image_size": [1238, 1632], "ocr": [{"text": "117", "bbox": [1173.7, 1587.4, 1198.4, 1604.1]}, {"text": "Unum 2015 Annual Report", "bbox": [977.9, 1587.7, 1132.8, 1604.0]}, {"text": "Mortgage Loans", "bbox": [112.5, 224.0, 297.8, 256.7]}, {"text": "Our mortgage loan portfolio is well diversified by both geographic region and property type to reduce risk of concentration. All of our", "bbox": [150.1, 262.5, 1153.0, 283.5]}, {"text": "mortgage loans are collateralized by commercial real estate. When issuing a new loan, our general policy is not to exceed a loan-to-value", "bbox": [112.5, 291.7, 1150.4, 312.7]}, {"text": "ratio, or the ratio of the loan balance to the estimated fair value of the underlying collateral, of 75 percent. We update the loan-to-value", "bbox": [112.5, 320.9, 1135.2, 341.9]}, {"text": "ratios at least every three years for each loan, and properties undergo a general inspection at least every two years. Our general policy for", "bbox": [112.5, 350.1, 1157.1, 371.1]}, {"text": "newly issued loans is to have a debt service coverage ratio greater than 1.25 times on a normalized 25 year amortization period. We", "bbox": [112.5, 379.3, 1112.9, 400.3]}, {"text": "update our debt service coverage ratios annually.", "bbox": [112.5, 408.5, 481.8, 429.5]}, {"text": "Mortgage loans by property type and geographic region are presented below.", "bbox": [150.1, 437.7, 736.6, 458.6]}, {"text": "December 31", "bbox": [801.0, 479.1, 891.3, 497.7]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [682.7, 507.1, 722.6, 525.9]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [983.4, 507.2, 1017.4, 525.9]}, {"text": "(in millions of dollars)", "bbox": [112.5, 535.3, 268.9, 554.0]}, {"text": "Carrying Amount", "bbox": [562.8, 535.3, 679.9, 554.0]}, {"text": "Percent of Total", "bbox": [721.8, 535.3, 830.0, 554.0]}, {"text": "Carrying Amount", "bbox": [862.9, 535.3, 980.1, 554.0]}, {"text": "Percent of Total", "bbox": [1021.9, 535.3, 1125.5, 554.0]}, {"text": "Property Type", "