u0007Borrower’s financial strength", "bbox": [150.1, 1421.6, 375.6, 1442.6]}, {"text": "• \u0007Borrower’s equity in transaction", "bbox": [150.1, 1450.8, 400.5, 1471.8]}, {"text": "• \u0007Additional collateral, if any", "bbox": [150.1, 1480.0, 359.0, 1501.0]}]}